data.title: DN5 Group
data.meta_description:
DN5 Group | 6,543 followers on LinkedIn. Subsea Specialist Air & Saturation Diving, NDT, ROV, Vessel Chartering, Indian Military Support. Ship Building & Repair. | DN5 Group is ISO registered internationally recognized engineering firm having five major operational sectors:-

Marine : Offshore SAT-AIR Diving & NDT, FPSO Support, Survey & Engg Services.
Defence : Ship & Submarine -Building Repair & Maintenance.  
Renergie : Offshore Wind Energy, Solar Ground Mounted & Rooftop.
data.text: I had the privilege of representing DN5 Group along with my CMD & Offshore Tech Suptd at a significant meeting with ONGC Videsh Ltd ONGC Petro additions Limited ONGC Foundation #ongc, where 40 companies participated. It was an excellent opportunity to showcase our company's capabilities and engage with industry leaders. Grateful for the chance to be a part of such a high profiled professional gathering and look forward to the potential collaborations and advancements that will follow. #DN5 #marine #ongc #professional #11highs #dn5marine #dn5group #dn5marinebestplacetowork #bestplacetowork.
